text:
Credit life insurance, credit accident and health insurance, and credit involuntary unemployment insurance shall be issued only in the following forms:
(1) individual policies of life insurance issued to debtors on the term plan;
(2) individual policies of accident and health insurance issued to debtors on a term plan or disability benefit provisions in individual policies of credit life insurance;
(3) individual policies of involuntary unemployment insurance issued to debtors on the term plan;
(4) group policies of life insurance issued to creditors providing insurance upon the lives of debtors on the term plan;
(5) group policies of accident and health insurance issued to creditors on a term plan insuring debtors or disability benefit provisions in group credit life insurance policies to provide such coverage;
(6) group policies of involuntary unemployment insurance issued to creditors on a term plan insuring debtors.
